**CHANGE app button — OnSelect full rewrite:**
```
If(
    !IsEmpty(Filter(Registrations, Session.psquad_eventsplansid = ThisItem.psquad_eventsplansid && UserEmail = User().Email)),
    UserUnregisterCancel.Run(
        LookUp(Registrations, Session.psquad_eventsplansid = ThisItem.psquad_eventsplansid && UserEmail = User().Email).UserEventID,
        User().Email,
        ThisItem.'Event Title'
    );
    Remove(Registrations, LookUp(Registrations, Session.psquad_eventsplansid = ThisItem.psquad_eventsplansid && UserEmail = User().Email)),
    Patch(Registrations, Defaults(Registrations),
        { psquad_title: ThisItem.'Event Title' & " - " & User().Email, Session: ThisItem, UserEmail: User().Email, 'Status (psquad_status)': 'Status (Registrations)'.Registered }
    )
);
Refresh(Registrations)
```

Register branch unchanged. Unregister branch now: call flow (pass UserEventID + email + title) → THEN remove row.

